cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object detection in indoor environments using deep Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN). 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions the enabling functionalities for service robots. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another likely category as the paper deals with training state-of-the-art object detectors using synthetically generated composite images. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category as the paper deals with training deep learning models for object detection. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper involves superimposing 2D images of textured object models into images of real environments.
